data.description: Great duplex opportunity.  One unit is currently rented and one unit is being used by the owners.  Keep the current situation and reduce your living expenses or have a great cash flow property by renting both units out.  There is also space on the lot to build more units.  There is plenty of opportunities with this very unique property.  Both units in the duplex have been recently remodeled and feature open floorplans and faux wood flooring.  Higher ceilings and spacious living areas allow for natural lighting.
